{"tid":693271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【官方認證】環時：美國對華為防範排擠 行為有失公正 ","createTime":"2018-06-07T10:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T00:28:33.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0ffd7e68ecf0edf36298e567cd2b1e65f2e5ba3e","tid":693271,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"【官媒出口術】環時：美國對華為防範排擠 行為有失公正&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1528354403118&amp;issue=20180607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1528354403118%26issue%3D20180607&d=vGq%2Bnr1PS76k8%2FORFM7KfXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=751d0d5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1528354403118%26issue%3D20180607&h=5b705afb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1528354403118&amp;issue=20180607</a><br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》社評指，Facebook(fb) 準備終止與華為的數據共享協議，是美國對中國公司，尤其是對華為的警惕和排擠升級的跡象。《環時》批評，美方此舉對華為嚴重有失公正，對fb也會造成損失，而美國對中國IT公司的高調防範，亦為世界作出很壞的示範。<br />\n<br />\n該社評又稱，微軟、英特爾、高通等公司軟硬件在中國的應用無處不在，蘋果手機在中國精英群體中的使用率亦非常高。《環時》質疑這些公司究竟在中國收集了多少數據，對中國訊息安全又是否已構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n《環時》又指，美國反覆打著安全牌的旗號，原因是出於政客們的無知和極端民族主義，還有部分原因是一些人把國家安全當成在國際貿易中耍賴的理由。文章指，華為製造的很多設備已優於美國公司的同類產品，排斥華為是美國的貿易保護主義作祟。<br />\n<br />\n文章又批評，美國打壓華為等中國製造商，是給蘋果等美國公司在中國市場挖坑，美國的做法是在破壞IT產業的全球生態，當其他國家的IT公司被一點點剝奪互聯網時代的基本生存條件後，美國的大型IT公司的生存資源亦必走向枯竭。<br />\n<br />\n此前英國《金融時報》報道，fb與逾60家公司有數據共享協議 ，當中至少涉及4間中國科技公司，包括華為、聯想、廣東歐珀移動通信和TCL集團。fb透露，可能於本周結束與華為的協議。"},{"pid":"139b4da0f9a4fd1675cfacd110ac9ebe094e92cf","tid":693271,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T11:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n環時撐，美國可以郁手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46ede9402cf9bbdc9f71f2eeab7bcdd11af05ad","tid":693271,"uid":33267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T11:03:51.000Z","msg":"講多無謂，禁撚咗iPhone呀笨!"},{"pid":"4fa5c47176d918d7bd494b9b823653fc16dff100","tid":693271,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T11:03:53.000Z","msg":"怕美國偷資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔撚好用囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7177c9e04d3e6933523f8d4d9db68523ad51db9","tid":693271,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T11:04:20.000Z","msg":"美帝固然唔公正<br />\n但你贏國咪又係?<br />\n打和啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee250188df9499f74c85876a628d8da9ff46af1f","tid":693271,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T11:09:27.000Z","msg":"佢自己咪一樣用政策手段迫外企交晒大陸地區用戶嘅資料比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有口話人&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3695cb4acd6588dc4a177ba833912b4e3c4e09b","tid":693271,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T11:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4a8d29138504a3e4a45fca36d2